Localization.Name: Medivac Rescue Light
Localization.Description: Manufacturer: RSI\n\nUtilizing multiple vibrant lights housed in a compact durable frame, the Rescue Light is capable at being seen from all directions in all kinds of hazardous atmospheric conditions, letting rescue teams know exactly where you are.
